name: Cameron Diaz
description:
A TI of the little-known, obscure American actress Cameron Diaz.

Works very well at Strength 1. Given Ms. Diaz's propensity to wear thin clothing with no bra there were a lot of 'pokies' in the training data, so negative prompting may be required to remove.

Also, her heyday was the mid-to-late 90's when 512x512 images were "High Res", so many of the training images are from her later years. Despite this it seems to work well, especially if adding an approximate age you want her to look.

modelVersions.name: v1.0
modelVersions.description:
This was a lot of work - 104 images, 20 vectors per token, 21,000 steps at a learning rate of 0.0015. But I'm impressed by the results, even if I say so myself.

The 'hit rate' is above 80% - seriously, the sample images here were mostly just the same prompt with Prompt S/R on to change her clothes and I was spoiled for choice!
